SAE certified, SAE stands for society of automotive engineers, all the lights are passed through SAE only after they pass certain tests to prove their quality standard
DOT Certified Lights: DOT stands for department of transportation which certifies that the lights can be used on roads for driving purposes and is totally legal
8LED with DRL and indicator lighting now your headlight also glows to give turning indication like side lights
Works in 2 modes high beam at 90W and low beam at 70W
The DRL gives you an elegant yet catchy look along with turning indication in headlight can be used for mountain driving, fog driving, highway driving, city driving, giving signals and making you visible from a long distance
Made from die casted aluminium, which makes it heavy duty, non-breakable, anti rust and gives it the ability to withstand heavy impacts
PMMA lens glass reflector on top makes it extremely powerful, bright with very strong penetration and increases visibility up to 200 metres
The carefully engineered design allows excellent heat dissipation to ensure long lasting life

On/Off Switch

Premium quality ABS plastic shell which has crisp on/off mechanism
Can be used with in many ways with auxiliary lights like U2 fog light, 9 LED light, USB charger, horns, sirens, hooters etc
Proper mounting to be installed on handlebar – if installed properly, remains tightly fixed
It comes with a short circuit mechanism to prevent hazard and also is engineered for proper Heat dissipation
Perfect for all biking activities
